{{link-en|印度地质调查局|Survey of India}}负责印度全部地形图的控制、测量及制图<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://dst.gov.in/scientific_services/survey.htm |title=Department of Scientific and Technology: Survey of India |accessdate=2008-02-16 |archive-date=2007-01-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070111193635/http://dst.gov.in/scientific_services/survey.htm |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

