115184057/http://akosarev.info/engine/?interface=geo_maps&form=main | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.warsawto.com/bbs/read.php?tid=39393&page= | title = 昔日秘密——互联网上的苏联军用基本比例尺地图 | author = eliter | publisher = 华约军事论坛}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = http://nav.lom.name/maps_scan/ | title = scan maps | publisher = nav.lom.name/maps_scan/ | access-date = 2021-05-29 | archive-date = 2021-02-11 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210211162120/http://nav.lom.name/maps_scan/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>

